        "generated_at": { "$ref": "#/$defs/timestamp" }
      },
      "$comment": "The protected registrar emits this attested receipt only after appending one canonical resolution record beneath resolutions/. Policy verifies the protected parent-to-child commit, unique absent path, immutable bytes/reference, exact later passing evidence and producer provenance, one-time resolution of the named debt, and no mutation of prior debts or resolutions."
    },
